snippet.title: CorpoNation: The Sorting Process Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Greetings valued employee! You have been tasked with sorting the Ringo CorpoNation’s genetic samples. We know you’ll give 110% when CorpoNation launches on Steam later this year!

Wishlist: https://bit.ly/CorpoNationSteam 
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/xWAeeah8dS
Find out more: https://www.CorpoNation.co.uk
